reviews.review_text:
JBG encore IS here! The track listings for this kickass AUD get off kilter in what's listed as a 17:19 St. Stephen.  In actuality, the Stephen ends at the 8:12 mark and the drummers promptly begin pounding out the NFA beat at the 8:14 mark.  From there, the Druns is the 4:45 track, the Terrapin is the 9:54 track, the Dew is the 13:32 track, and the set-closing Sugar Mag, the 10:02 track. The JBG is the final 4:22 track.
The only bump here is the beginning of Stephen getting clipped.  Otherwise, this fine AUD pull sparkles!

Michael Johann   Michael from Riverside Ca was one of my first taper friends.
